## Limitations
This report is based on a limited selection of articles from Forbes, which may not capture the full spectrum of business adaptations during the COVID-19 pandemic. Additionally, the focus on Forbes as a single source may introduce bias, as other publications might offer different perspectives or additional insights. The findings are also constrained by the availability of articles within the search results, which may not represent the most recent developments in business strategies post-pandemic.

